lead_paragraph: West Bromwich Albion's Chris Brunt said he was "ashamed" of his club's supporters after being struck under the eye by a coin thrown by a fan after their surprise 3-1 defeat at Reading in the FA Cup on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Brunt 'Ashamed' of WBA Fans After Hit by Coin
